{"tid":1480080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台同心 支持美國對台售武","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:38:43.000Z","uid":165683,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f55beec03dc00cf1539bc3a0d34920a170fbc76","tid":1480080,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475197-20190817.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475197-20190817.htm&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=65a2d316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475197-20190817.htm&h=68f17b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475197-20190817.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國政府推進向台灣出售總值80億美元的F-16戰機計劃，在台灣，蔡英文總統認為，將一定程度提升台灣空軍戰力與整體防衛能量，形容軍購是為了防衛需求，「錢都會花在刀口上」；又說，在足夠自我防衛力量下，才能保證，和平可以持續下去。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文到台中市參觀一間科技公司後表示，感謝美國行政部門採取正面態度，認為體現美國行政與國會機關根據《台灣關係法》，讓台灣有足夠的自我防衛能力。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨籍參議員魯比奧早前證實，白宮已決定，將對台出售66架F-16戰機的計劃，提交國會審查。"},{"pid":"cc306351e78b2551ea8be2078841fe5c44f65439","tid":1480080,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"中國外交部今天舉行例行記者會，發言人耿爽則表示，中方對美方有關動向表示嚴重關切，呼籲美方慎重妥處涉台問題，以免嚴重損害中美關係和台海和平穩定。"},{"pid":"95070ec5eb5a85b5fd867439c5a285a83629983a","tid":1480080,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"賣埋THAAD、F-15 嗰啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b2b5a3da4133a09ec91ee1f3d2b49881c647fd","tid":1480080,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc306351e78b2551ea8be2078841fe5c44f65439","tid":1480080,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":